title: 04 — Containers (Open, Close, Lock, Unlock, Put In, Take From)
story: regression
author: Sharpee Regression Suite
description: Verify openable, lockable container with key, put in, and take from

---

# Get the key and flashlight first
> take key
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> take flashlight
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Turn on flashlight so we can see in the dark closet
> switch on flashlight
[OK: contains "on"]

# Go to the supply closet (dark room)
> south
[OK: contains "Supply Closet"]

# The toolbox is here — try to open it (locked)
> open toolbox
[OK: contains "locked"]

# Unlock it with the key
> unlock toolbox with key
[OK: contains "unlock"]

# Now open it
> open toolbox
[OK: contains "open"]

# Look inside — wrench should be there
> look in toolbox
[OK: contains "wrench"]

# Take the wrench
> take wrench
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Put the key in the toolbox
> put key in toolbox
[OK: contains "put"]

# Verify key is inside
> look in toolbox
[OK: contains "key"]

# Close the toolbox
> close toolbox
[OK: contains "closed"]

# Lock it
> lock toolbox with key
